  <section class="regulations-section">
    <h2>1. General Provisions</h2>
    <p>
      These Regulations define the rules for using the event platform, including user roles,
      account creation, and data processing.
    </p>

    <h2>2. User Responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Users must provide accurate personal information during registration.</li>
      <li>It is forbidden to upload unlawful or offensive content.</li>
      <li>Users must respect event cancellation policies set by organizers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      User data is stored securely and processed only for the purposes of event participation
      and platform functionality. Detailed information is available in the Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Final Provisions</h2>
    <p>
      The platform administrators reserve the right to update these Regulations.
      Users will be notified of any significant changes via email.
    </p>
  </section>